        public void showSelectedEdgeInfo​(java.lang.String subsystem1,
                                 java.lang.String subsystem2,
                                 java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> interfaceNames)
        Updates the selection info at the top of the tab.

        The subsystems names will be shown as labels, while the interface names will be shown as scrollable list.

        Parameters:
        subsystem1 - the name of the first subsystem
        subsystem2 - the name of the second subsystem
        interfaceNames - the interface names to be shown in a scrollable list

      • showSelectedSubsystemInfo

        public void showSelectedSubsystemInfo​(java.lang.String subsystemName,
                                      int numberOfMetabolites,
                                      int numberOfReactions)
        Updates the selection info at the top of the tab.

        The name o fthe selected subsystem will be shown, as well as the number of reactions and metabolites contained in it.

        Parameters:
        subsystemName - the name of the selected subsystem
        numberOfMetabolites - the number of metabolites contained in the currently selected subsystem
        numberOfReactions - the number of reactions contained in the currently selected subsystem
